description:
NLC Introduction: NLC Token is a global universal integration published by NLC Wallet, or NLC for short. NLC is based on the decentralized digital assets released by Ethereum, using the Tokenomics model, accompanied by a repurchase and destruction mechanism, with the goal of connecting excellent digital asset projects with NLC quality users, professional investors, etc. The creation of the NLC ecological closed loop. Realize the win-win situation of the industry in the global blockchain era, and jointly promote the healthy development of the blockchain and digital asset industry. As the eco-coin of NLC Wallet, NLC can be used and distributed in many scenarios of NLC Ecology.
The purpose is to enable users to enjoy more.
